(48, 1, '2023-04-11 15:29:18', '2023-04-11 15:29:18', 'Viggo Peter Mortensen Jr. born October 20, 1958) is an American actor, writer, director, producer, musician, and multimedia artist. Born and raised in the State of New York to a Danish father and American mother, he also lived in Argentina during his childhood. He is the recipient of various accolades including a Screen Actors Guild Award and has been nominated for three Academy Awards, three BAFTA Awards, and four Golden Globe Awards.', 'Viggo Mortensen', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'viggo-mortensen', '', '', '2023-04-11 15:29:18', '2023-04-11 15:29:18', '', 0, 'http://tmdb_actor_id=110', 0, 'actors', '', 0),
