(472, 1, '2023-04-11 15:55:54', '2023-04-11 15:55:54', 'Junko Nakajima (中島 淳子 Nakajima Junko, born 2 May 1952), more commonly known by her stage name Mari Natsuki (夏木 マリ Natsuki Mari), is a Japanese singer, dancer and actress. Born in Tokyo, she started work as a singer from a young age. In 2007 she announced her engagement to percussionist Nobu Saitō, with their marriage taking place in Spring 2008.', 'Mari Natsuki', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mari-natsuki', '', '', '2023-04-11 15:55:54', '2023-04-11 15:55:54', '', 0, 'http://tmdb_actor_id=19589', 0, 'actors', '', 0),
